data.title: Wayland, New York Population 2024
data.text:
Poverty in Wayland

The race most likely to be in poverty in Wayland is Hispanic , with 85.82% below the poverty level.

The race least likely to be in poverty in Wayland is Other , with 4.88% below the poverty level.

The poverty rate among those that worked full-time for the past 12 months was 1.92% . Among those working part-time, it was 22.3% , and for those that did not work, the poverty rate was 20.55% .
